## Getting Started

### Using Dev Container (Recommended)

1. Clone the governance workspace (if not already):
   ```bash
   git clone <governance-repo-url> my-workspace
   cd my-workspace
   ```

2. Clone this project into the workspace:
   ```bash
   git clone <this-repo-url> project/
   ```

3. Open `project/` in VS Code and select **Reopen in Container** when prompted.

4. Inside the container, dependencies are installed automatically via `postCreateCommand`.

### Local Development (Without Dev Container)

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Run tests
npm test
```

