## AI Development

This project uses the [OpenCode Governance Framework](../README.md) for AI-assisted development. The governance wrapper provides:

- **Backlog-Planner** agent for planning work items
- **Change-Orchestrator** agent for implementation

See `../README.md` for details on the two-agent workflow.
